(42, 19, 46, 19, 93, 5, 5, 'house of prayer', 'House of the Lord', 'Both passages emphasize the sanctity of God''s house. Luke highlights its intended purpose as a ''house of prayer,'' while Psalms affirms that ''holiness becometh thine house.''', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
