(42, 20, 1, 41, 11, 27, 33, 'in the temple', 'Authority in the Temple', 'Both passages emphasize the confrontation between Jesus and the religious leaders in the temple. They highlight the questioning of Jesus'' authority, illustrating the tension between him and the chief priests, scribes, and elders.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 20, 1, 42, 8, 1, 1, 'preached the gospel', 'Preaching and Teaching Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the act of preaching, with Jesus teaching the people in the temple and going throughout cities and villages to proclaim the gospel. This connection highlights the continuity of Jesus'' mission to spread the glad tidings of the kingdom of God.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
